OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPakistan appeals to world  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor aid amid flood crisis  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Pakistan is appealing for further      
OL,6, international assistance after floods  
OL,7, wreaked havoc across the country.      
OL,9,FThe US, UK, United Arab Emirates and   
OL,10,Fothers have contributed to a monsoon   
OL,11,Fdisaster appeal but more funds are     
OL,12,Fneeded, an interior ministry official  
OL,13,Ftold the BBC.                          
OL,15,FMore than 1,000 people have died and   
OL,16,Fmillions have been displaced since     
OL,17,FJune, Salman Sufi said.                
OL,19,FHe said Pakistan's government was doing
OL,20,Feverything in its power to help people.
